{"tid":1004150,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今天不小心把心愛的水杯打碎了🥺","createTime":"2019-02-01T08:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T12:41:32.000Z","uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4cdf267407a0e286b55750c27d5e37f3afd4491f","tid":1004150,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T08:31:03.000Z","msg":"事後我用了十五分鐘去細心欣賞 <br />\n發現打碎了的玻璃碎 <br />\n竟然比起平日那個形態更美☺️<br />\n然後我再用了十分鐘去打掃地方 <br />\n再為其拍照📸<br />\n<br />\n這短短的三十分鐘 <br />\n算是今天我思緒最安穩的時間 <br />\n打碎了的水杯 <br />\n是我今天看過最美好的東西 <br />\n而那水杯著地的那一聲 <br />\n是聽過最美好的聲音 🥰<br />\n<br />\n原來人生覺得最爛的事情 <br />\n也未必是最糟 <br />\n因為最糟的 <br />\n可能一直就在眼前而未曾發現 <br />\n又或者根本就是自己 <br />\n我想我找到了答案😉"},{"pid":"34b01d58bb2c2b28b5e5a21fa55ba4b98fedc4f4","tid":1004150,"uid":81919,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T08:32:24.000Z","msg":"屌你柒頭，loop夠未"},{"pid":"f58066796025345e78ecee279331fcc282c6556a","tid":1004150,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34b01d58bb2c2b28b5e5a21fa55ba4b98fedc4f4","tid":1004150,"uid":81919,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T08:32:24.000Z","msg":"屌你柒頭，loop夠未"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T08:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38975d51f14fda5d627d1dea541d84eeadaefde8","tid":1004150,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T08:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a744d1404ee90c57b2270ea61b11357a76f3ab2","tid":1004150,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T12:41:32.000Z","msg":"做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}